78}, {\"ngram\": \"a fifth medal\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On top of his Olympic credentials, Le Clos has an incredible record in other FINA events and has been particularly dominant in short course swimming down the years.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic credentials\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible record\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"other FINA events\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"short course\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 32-year-old takes to the water in the 100m butterfly and admits that he has a lot to do to keep up with the next generation of top swimmers.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"butterfly\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"top swimmers\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Clos is racing hurt after picking up a muscular injury in training for the games, but refused to let that stand in the way of him turning out in Paris.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999964011295, \"rank\": 3.5990883264648547e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"a muscular injury\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the third oldest male swimmer at these Games, so in those terms I am something of a pensioner,\\\" Le Clos toldTEAM SOUTH AFRICA.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third oldest male swimmer\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"those terms\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"a pensioner\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"toldTEAM\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"SOUTH AFRICA\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And in spite of picking up a shoulder tear in training, I have come to Paris believing I have a chance.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999964011295, \"rank\": 3.5990883264648547e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spite\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"a shoulder tear\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have raced with injuries before.\\\"\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Clos believes that if he can break through the heats and get himself into the semi-finals, he will have a shot at making a final where anything could happen.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"